      "content": "the truth is i don't think i'm just \"not in touch\" with myself. it's more like... the person i was is gone too. he was the part of me that actually lived. now i'm just a shell. everything feels so pointless. if the most important thing in my life is gone, what's the point of staying in this empty house just to wait for the clock to run out? it feels like i'm just waiting for a movie to end when the main character has already died.",
